Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.96,0:02:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭髮睡得好亂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前開始就覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部再注意一下頭髮就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得長得這麼可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.19,0:02:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 丘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 怎麼啦你的頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭髮睡得很亂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭髮…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有這麼嚴重嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然也很像卜部的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:03:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子必須注意下頭髮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺 很刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你總是用劉海遮住眼睛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前就在想了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部改變髮型露出眼睛的話 形象會改變很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部 這麼難得 要不今天整天都保持這個髮型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露出眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:03:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都認不出是誰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部 束起劉海很不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我梳的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然頭一回看到卜部束起劉海的樣子 還挺可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然至今都認為她是個怪人 但今天的得分很高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要不要去追卜部呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼啦那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是想去廁所嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天也是這個髮型去學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.62,0:05:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為弄這個髮型的是丘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丘明天也弄我的頭髮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許會變成這個髮型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天開始不要弄這個髮型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想你變回原來的髮型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要問為什麼 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾只有我能看到的卜部的素面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想讓大家看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把雙手給我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雙手？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:05:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要幹啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這雙手將我的頭髮盡情弄亂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再用力點 弄到很亂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 原來的髮型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿不喜歡那個髮型的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣看過去 感覺這個髮型對我來說才是最可愛的髮型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被椿弄亂頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺有點舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那臺詞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得有點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想到了跟卜部很相稱的新髮型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃完便當去更衣室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天的形象改變 不是得到班裡的好評嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那是義大利面熏肉卷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以作為主食的新烹調法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也挑戰一下新髮型好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都說免了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 卜部被椿說變回原來的髮型了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然好像是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為椿獨佔欲好像很強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獨佔欲？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿對因變了髮型 而被其它男生看到卜部的素面這事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很討厭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺 心跳得很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:10:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部 昨天被椿說變回原來的髮型的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓椿做了很舒服的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒服的事情…怎樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能用雙手抓住我的頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.76,0:10:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為啥要做這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理由你就別管了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:10:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後能就這樣攪亂我的頭髮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之試試
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼鏡起霧了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被喜歡的人弄亂頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺有點舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那兩人 總是做些奇怪的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一張300円買不買
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前卜部不是換過一天的髮型嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天我偷拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧 竟然做到那個地步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.03,0:12:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為很罕見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新看一看 卜部果然很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要這張
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 300円
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平時前發遮著眼睛都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要這張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別推我別推我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這群混蛋公狗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在身為男朋友的我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,買賣連我都很少見到的卜部的素面的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺很火大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想現在就對這群傢伙宣言 卜部是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:12:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面目猙獰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一臉著急的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去廁所嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是那種表情嗎 這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為真的很不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部明明是我的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只屬於我的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道我的獨佔欲很強嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿 上野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們不要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為男朋友的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想要「大家都有的照片」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其實我真的很想要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經有丘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺這樣看著卜部 是不是有點像今井百夏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說起來還真是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 這種有點銳利的眼神非常像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很像很像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 是不是很像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確很像今井百夏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像卜部的女孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個… 今井百夏是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我們同校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 人家是偶像啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個啦 最近因為飲用水廣告紅起來的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個廣告很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我買了寫真集
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這張照片真的很像今井百夏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然比起百夏 有點冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來有個很像卜部的偶像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼椿 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 平時的話都會這麼直接回家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但今天回家之前先去書店
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很像卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去結帳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我買了買了 我就買下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想趕緊回去看裡面的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 這不是椿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真少見啊 居然會在書店碰見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你買什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今井百夏的寫真集啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為聽說是最近成為話題的偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺偶爾看看這些流行物也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.82,0:15:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過話說回來 真的很像卜部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有泳衣的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸部是卜部的更大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.24,0:16:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是這也有可愛之處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部就是這種滿臉的笑容很少見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,買了好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在男生之間販賣著卜部同學的照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攝影部不是有個叫中島的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙用一張300円的價格在賣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢 公平買了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒買
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有丘在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那椿呢 椿買了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那傢伙也沒買
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是椿其實很喜歡卜部那種樣子的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會知道那種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為在剛才那個書店 那傢伙買了今井百夏的寫真集
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:17:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今井百夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今井百夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部同學長得很像今井百夏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今井百夏是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在當紅的偶像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很像我的偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿也買了這個人的寫真集
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天聽上野說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是長得很像卜部同學才買的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長得好像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 卜部 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿有今井百夏的寫真集吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽丘同學說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上野-丘-卜部的路線嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早知道就封住上野的口了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個偶像很像我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.26,0:19:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我買了那個人的寫真集是因為她長得很像卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說會喜歡上那個偶像是因為我喜歡卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…怎麼說呢 呃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想看那個寫真集
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在那個公園裡等你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能把那個寫真集拿來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 是吧 長得很像卜部對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己看也這樣覺得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.49,0:20:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這本寫真集裡椿最喜歡的照片是哪張？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…我最喜歡的照片是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.45,0:20:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿 保持這樣不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道要發動內褲剪刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿是我的男朋友
